        "message": "Patch Set 5: -Code-Review\n\n> (2 comments)\n\nIf that's the case, then I think we should modify the PolicyIdentXxx classes to NOT be subclassed from PfConceptKey, but to be simple POJOs, and then modify these classes to use those.",
